ZH: 这个问题你要怎么管？
EN: How are you going to handle this problem?

ZH: 他总是自私，不会为别人着想。
EN: He's always selfish and doesn't care about others.

ZH: 她管不住自己的脾气，总是发火。
EN: She can't control her temper and always loses control.

ZH: 请不要管我的事情。
EN: Please don't interfere with my business.

ZH: 别管我！我自己能做。
EN: Don't bother me! I can do it myself.

ZH: 我会照顾好这个孩子的。
EN: I will take care of this child.

ZH: 他管着公司的财务部门。
EN: He's in charge of the finance department of the company.

ZH: 老板让我负责这个项目的进度。
EN: The boss asked me to be in charge of the progress of this project.

ZH: 我们应该怎样处理这个紧急情况？
EN: How should we deal with this emergency situation?

ZH: 这件事情必须要立刻解决。
EN: This matter must be resolved immediately.

ZH: 请你帮我处理这个文件。
EN: Please help me handle this document.

ZH: 我会得到家人的支持的。
EN: I will get the support of my family.

ZH: 他总是关心别人的感受。
EN: He always cares about other people's feelings.

ZH: 请你不要打扰他。
EN: Please do not disturb him.

ZH: 我们一起来解决这个问题吧。
EN: Let's solve this problem together.

ZH: 怎么才能管好我的时间？
EN: How can I manage my time well?

ZH: 改变无法控制的事情是徒劳的。
EN: It is useless to try to control what cannot be controlled.

ZH: 我们必须要采取行动了。
EN: We must take action now.

ZH：你应该学会自己照顾好自己。
EN: You should learn to take care of yourself.
